'''OneKey''' is a worldwide healthcare professionals database developed by [[Cegedim Relationship Management]]. Cegedim was acquired by IMS Health in April 2015. 
The OneKey database is available in 73 countries and contains more than 13.7 million Healthcare Professionals<ref name="IMS Health">[IMS Health OneKey database]</ref>

OneKey is updated by phone operators who validate the database, adhering to [[ISO 9001]] procedures.<ref name="IMS Health" />

OneKey is built according to the same unique data model in all countries.<ref name="IMS Health" />

